__NAME__ purpose
disallow tax calculations to apply negative value
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='plain'>
	<arg choice='plain'>0</arg>
	<arg choice='plain'>1</arg>
</group>
__END__


__NAME__ default
0
__END__


__NAME__ description
When the pragma is enabled and the &glos-tax; calculation yields a negative
number, the tax amount applied will be reset to zero.
__END__


__NAME__ example: Enable __FILENAME__
Put the following in &ccf;:
<programlisting>
Pragma no_negative_tax
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ see also
&glos-tax;
__END__

